Lead stocks held by U.S. refiners roseto 37,295 short tons at the end of February from 34,224 shorttons (revised higher) at the end of January, the AmericanBureau of Metal Statistics reported.    Production of lead decreased to 33,619 short tons inFebruary from 38,759 short tons in January.    Shipments from plants increased to 30,467 short tons inFebruary from 27,041 short tons (revised lower) in January, theABMS said. Reuter&#3;